{"tid":1026194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"79歲老翁荃灣行人天橋頂墮下　送院不治","createTime":"2019-02-18T02:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T07:40:11.000Z","uid":41404,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2c77b6a1e9968ba5f27c83ec44cb4efc71e9b6bd","tid":1026194,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T02:29:43.000Z","msg":"今日(18日)凌晨2時許，一名姓劉79歲老翁，被發現爬上荃灣海灣花園海雲閣對開行人天橋頂，疑一躍而下，跌至地面一個花槽旁，重傷昏迷，其頸巾及衣物散落一旁，保安員報警。救護員將劉送院急救，可惜證實不治。警方正聯絡家人，追查他輕生原因。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線： <br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222 <br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000 <br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288 <br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255 <br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000 <br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281 <br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350 <br />\n利民會： 3512 2626 <br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgM4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=b64c1f55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a>"},{"pid":"b1026e49567b26579dbd494a72d3d2b755bdcc2f","tid":1026194,"uid":158270,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T06:42:24.000Z","msg":"都老啦，想死唔俾佢死？"},{"pid":"776fabf139fbca091743aadc08987a383604b0b8","tid":1026194,"uid":199138,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b1026e49567b26579dbd494a72d3d2b755bdcc2f","tid":1026194,"uid":158270,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T06:42:24.000Z","msg":"都老啦，想死唔俾佢死？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T07:02:08.000Z","msg":"政府會話佢仲係中年"},{"pid":"9ac5fa9cc87a3fefb27b11a0b5f5d12b9f9cf29e","tid":1026194,"uid":36115,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T07:03:33.000Z","msg":"而家d咁既新聞標題<br />\n唔睇內文以為係意外<br />\n唔講阿伯就唔係自殺咩"},{"pid":"8710670cd898f59974e0972a97c8110b730eb2ba","tid":1026194,"uid":158270,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9ac5fa9cc87a3fefb27b11a0b5f5d12b9f9cf29e","tid":1026194,"uid":36115,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T07: